com.samsung.android.sdk.pen.recognition

Interface SpenSignatureVerification.ResultListener

  • Enclosing class:
    SpenSignatureVerification

    public static interface SpenSignatureVerification.ResultListener
    This listener interface provides callback methods for getting signature recognition results.
    Register this listener to get results for the SpenSignatureVerification.request(List) method.
    See Also:
    SpenSignatureVerification.request(List), SpenSignatureVerification.setResultListener(ResultListener)

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onResult(List<SpenObjectStroke> input, boolean result)
      Called as a response to the SpenSignatureVerification.request(List) method.

    • Method Detail

      • onResult

        void onResult(List<SpenObjectStroke> input,
            boolean result)
        Called as a response to the SpenSignatureVerification.request(List) method.
        Parameters:
        input - The list of strokes of the input signature.
        result - Set to true if the input signature matches a registered signature, set to false if the input signature does not match a registered signature.
